teacheasy.data

Class GraphicObject

  • java.lang.Object
    • teacheasy.data.PageObject
      • teacheasy.data.GraphicObject

  • public class GraphicObject
extends PageObject
    Encapsulates the data that describes a Graphics Object as defined in the TeachEasy digital lesson XML format. Extends the page object supertype.
    Version:
    1.0 05 Feb 2015
    Author:
    Lewis Thresh, Calum Armstrong

             float nOutlineThickness,
             boolean nShadow,
             float nStartTime,
             float nDuration)
        Constructor to create the data object with the data parsed from XML.
        Parameters:
        nType - Graphic type.
        nXStart - Relative X axis start position.
        nYStart - Relative Y axis start position.
        nXEnd - Relative X axis end position.
        nYEnd - Relative Y axis end position.
        nRotation - Rotation in degrees.
        nGraphicColor - Colour of the graphic in #AARRGGBB format.
        nSolid - Solid setting.
        nLineColor - Outline colour in #AARRGGBB format.
        nOutlineThickness - Outline thickness.
        nShadow - Shadow setting.
        nStartTime - Start time (not used).
        nDuration - Duration (not used).
